data.description: Lovely 4 bed/3 bath home in midtown Conway with updated hard wood floors in all living areas and tile in wet areas. As you enter the front door, you are greeted a spacious separate dining room mirrored across with a formal living room or library. Large living room offers plenty of space for entertaining and features a tray ceiling, can lights, and gas log fireplace. Living room is open to the eat in kitchen which offers granite counters, tile backsplash, pantry with pull out shelves, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. Split floor plan offers two bedrooms on each side of the house. Primary bedroom is incredibly spacious and features a tray ceiling. Primary Bath offers double vanity with granite counters, soaking tub, walk in shower, walk in closets, and private toilet room. Second bedroom and another full bathroom are on same side of house. Across the house, you'll find two bedrooms each with wood floors and a jack and jill bath with tiled accent wall and double vanity. Don't forget to check out the not one but 2 coat closets and linen closets in the home as well as a separate laundry room. Exterior features include two car garage, fully (new) fenced backyard, & patio.
